~FT   Synopsis~RS : This is the second wiz level.  This level contains 
              more commands that enable the user to use disciplinary 
              measures according to the owners standards or preferences.  
              Users at this level are generally also encouraged to 
              participate in advertising, etc..  Promotions  are based 
              on the same criteria as lower wiz levels. 

